{"tid":292073,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"CUBA籃球美少女 顏值高 身材好","createTime":"2017-06-21T05:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T18:59:09.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1723d196d36c7c20ed3fbe59bba9b065c386d98","tid":292073,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"林雪慧（小慧）曾經係CUBA（中國大學生籃球賽）女籃隊員，但因為傷病而退隊，不過佢仍然會以攝影嘅身份現身籃球場。噚日有中國新浪網就放咗小慧嘅一批相出嚟，當中有一佢打波嘅短片，仲話「打籃球的姑娘就一定身材不好嗎？可是，她也打籃球呀&hellip;&hellip;」明顯係為小慧抱不平，又話如果想同小慧做朋友，首先要確定自己喺球場上打唔得打得贏佢！<br />\n<br />\n小慧今日都有喺微博轉載呢個post，佢除咗多謝新浪體育，仲留言「可能要打一輩子籃球」，非常搞笑。唔少網友就留言大讚小慧有樣有身材又有技術，稱呼佢做女神，不過亦有人留言話小慧帶波撞人非常難防。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170621&amp;guid=56856173&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170621%26guid%3D56856173%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant&d=8eAG5A1w8i1IXExU1jg3cLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=83c173af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170621%26guid%3D56856173%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant&h=93d3764d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170621&amp;guid=56856173&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170621/large/1498013775_de0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170621%2Flarge%2F1498013775_de0e.jpg&h=5cab6716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170621/large/1498013778_32b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170621%2Flarge%2F1498013778_32b1.jpg&h=9c02c632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170621/larg